## Quick Reference

### Design Tokens
- **Spacing**: SPACING[0-12]
- **Typography**: TEXT_STYLES (max 8 styles)
- **Colors**: theme.* (no hard-coded hex)
- **Radius**: BORDER_RADIUS (sm/md/lg)

### Component Tiers
- **Tier 1**: AppText (variant required)
- **Tier 2**: Surface/Card (surface type required)
- **Tier 3**: Button (variant required)

### Accessibility
- **Touch targets**: Min 44×44px
- **Contrast**: WCAG AA (4.5:1)
- **State**: Never color-only

### Screen Architecture
- **Wrapper**: ScreenWrapper component (all screens)
- **Padding**: SPACING[5] default (20px)
- **Safe Area**: Handled by wrapper

